SubjectAgreement regarding the Sharing of Forfeited or confiscated assets or their Equivalent Sums Canada-Bahamas
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Foreign Affairs to take the action necessary to bring into force for Canada the AGREEMENT between the Government of Canada and the Government of the Commonwealth of the Bahamas REGARDING THE SHARING OF FORFEITED OR CONFISCATED ASSETS OR THEIR EQUIVALENT SUMS.
